lead_paragraph: The Thailand-hosted King's Cup will mark its return to the schedule after a one-year absence in the last week of July as a co-sanctioned event with the European Tour, the Asia Tour said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: King's Cup Returns as Co-Sanctioned Event in Thailand
